### Example 3 — Definite Description Resolution

**Known entities:**
| Name | Type | Description |
|------|------|-------------|
| Rohan Shaw | Person | An AI engineer |
| TheLinkAI | Organization | An AI Solutions company |

**Existing facts (already extracted):**
| Subject | Predicate | Object | Confidence |
|---------|-----------|--------|------------|
| Rohan Shaw | works_at | TheLinkAI | 0.95 |
| Rohan Shaw | works_as | ai engineer | 0.9 |

**New message:**
```
Nikita is my colleague at the company.
```

**Expected output:**
```json
[
  {
    "subject": "Nikita",
    "predicate": "colleague_of",
    "object": "Rohan Shaw",
    "confidence": 0.9
  },
  {
    "subject": "Nikita",
    "predicate": "works_at",
    "object": "TheLinkAI",
    "confidence": 0.85
  }
