```

**Why this is correct:**
- `"Nikita"` is a new proper name — used as-is.
- `"my colleague"` is a definite description → resolved to the known Person
  `Rohan Shaw` (the only Person whose organization is TheLinkAI).
- `"the company"` is a definite description → resolved to the known Organization
  `TheLinkAI` (the only Organization in known entities).
- No generic "company" or "colleague" entities leak into the output.
- The existing fact `Rohan Shaw works_at TheLinkAI` is not re-extracted.

